text.tspan: Moosaa feels sorry for these kids and
while strolling through the forest late at
night, he sees a shooting star in the sky.
He immediately closes his eyes and
wishes for an environment similar to
what he had in his homeland, for these
kids, so they can stop staring at the
funny object and start playing with each
other to grow stronger and great individ
After having a sumptuous dinner of aquatic plants, he
falls asleep under a giant old tree. Soon enough, Moosaa
has a dream where he is in a land of mystical objects. He
climbs, rides, slides and jumps. He has never had so much
fun and frolic even at his home land. There were so many
kids and so many things to play with. Even though he is
exhausted with all the play, he doesn't want to stop play
ing or leave his friends. But then, a bright light blinds him
and interrupts his dream - The rising sun shine
Moosaa liked to travel around the snow
covered Scandinavian forests in the winter
and experience different habitats while
meeting new animals and human beings,
especially kids. His curiosity and enthusiasm
took him to lands far away and south.
Moosaa was an intelligent and fun-loving "Elk",
who lived in the northern lands of Norsemen. As a
kid, in his homeland, he used to run, jump, slide in
snow and swim with his friends which kept them
athletic and always together. The camaraderie
they built among each other grew everyday they
played together in the sun-streaming beautiful
woodlands. The kids' parents watched while they
played and taught them to share, to be nice to each
other and above all to have fun.
As he drifts away from his home land, he
realizes that the human kids are not
playing with each other but staring at
some funny object and talking to
themselves. In fact, it is their parents
who give these objects to keep the kids
busy. These kids lacked not only physical
strength but also basic interpersonal
skills.
Moosaa wakes up and realizes his
destiny. He calls the mystic land from his
dream "Moosaa Land" - A land of
never-ending fun where kids can - be kids
and with kids. A land of boundless energy
and intellect where kids become stronger
and learn to become noble. A land where
parents can safely watch and let their
kids show raw, uninhibited and godly
happiness!
